blogPost.excerpt: Not even the most optimistic of Arkansas fans could have predicted the incredible start the Hogs are off to in 2021.  After a huge win against Texas A&M that catapulted the Razorbacks into the AP top 10, Arkansas now has the tough task of moving out of the FBS basement and leave behind their friends of several years.
